title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.CALL_PHONE.description: Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.EXPAND_STATUS_BAR.description: Allows application to expand or collapse the status bar.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.ACCESS_NOTIFICATION_P.description: Marker permission for applications that wish to access notification policy.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN.description: Allows an application to configure the local Bluetooth phone and to discover and pair with remote devices.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 In order to improve your experience with our product, we are introducing our updated User Experience Personalization & Improvement Program. By participating the program, you will be offered with highly customized experience solution plan, including individualized ads and more. According to the policy of the program, this app will collect anonymous information about your phone and the usage of our app to improve your experience with it. The information is collected through Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, and Alibaba Umeng.

	This app also personalizes your advertising experience through Google Admob and Facebook Audience Network. By consenting to this enhanced ad experience, you will be provided with customized ads that Google and Facebook believe are more relevant to you. Depending on your privacy settings, Google and Facebook may collect and process personal data such as device identifiers, location data, and other demographic and interest data about you to provide this personalized advertising experience.

	By agreeing, you are confirming that you are over the age of 16 and would like to join our User Experience Personalization & Improvement Program.

	We highly respect your privacy and will not gather any personal information about you or your system.

	You may stop participating the program at any time by checking the Settings page."

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 Um Ihre Erfahrung mit unserem Produkt zu verbessern, wir stellen unser aktuelles Programm zur Personalisierung und Verbesserung der Benutzerfreundlichkeit vor. Durch die Teilnahme am Programm erhalten Sie einen maßgeschneiderten Lösungsplan, einschließlich individualisierter Werbung und mehr. Gemäß der Richtlinie des Programms sammelt diese App anonyme Informationen über Ihr Telefon und die Nutzung unserer App, um Ihre Erfahrung damit zu verbessern. Die Informationen werden über Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, und Alibaba Umeng gesammelt.

	Diese App personalisiert deine Werbeerfahrung durch Google Admob und Facebook Audience Network. Indem du dieser verbesserten Werbeerfahrung zustimmst, siehst du Anzeigen, die rung durch Google Admob und Facebook Audience Network für dich als relevant erachten. Abhängig von deinen Datenschutzeinstellungen können Google und Facebook personenbezogene Daten wie Gerätekennungen, Standortdaten und andere demografische Daten über dich sowie Informationen über deine Interessen sammeln und verarbeiten, um diese personalisierte Werbeerfahrung zu ermöglichen.

	Indem du zustimmst, bestätigst du, dass du über 16 Jahre alt bist und Sie möchten unser Programm zur Personalisierung und Verbesserung der Benutzerfreundlichkeit mitmachen.

	Wir respektieren Ihre Privatsphäre und sammeln keine persönlichen Informationen über Sie oder Ihr System. Sie können die Teilnahme am Programm jederzeit beenden, indem Sie auf der Seite Einstellungen nachsehen."

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 Om uw ervaring met ons product te verbeteren, brengen wij ons bijgewerkte Personalisatie- en Verbeteringsprogramma voor Gebruikerservaringen. Door aan het programma deel te nemen, ontvangt u een sterk gepersonaliseerd oplossingsplan voor ervaringen, waaronder geïndividualiseerde reclame en nog veel meer. Volgens het beleid van het programma, zal deze app anonieme informatie over uw telefoon en het gebruik van onze app verzamelen, om uw ervaring hiermee te verbeteren. De informatie wordt via Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, en Alibaba Umeng verzameld.

	Deze app personaliseert je advertentiebeleving via Google Admob en Facebook Audience Network. Als je akkoord gaat met deze verbeterde advertentiebeleving, zie je advertenties waarvan Google Admob en Facebook Audience Network geloven dat deze beter bij je passen. Afhankelijk van je privacyinstellingen kunnen Google en Facebook persoonlijke gegevens zoals apparaat-id's, locatiegegevens en andere demografische en interessegegevens over jou verzamelen en verwerken, zodat deze gepersonaliseerde advertentiebeleving kan worden aangeboden.

	Door akkoord te gaan, bevestig je dat je minstens zestien jaar oud bent en u wilt deelnemen aan ons Personalisatie- en Verbeteringsprogramma voor Gebruikerservaringen.

	Wij respecteren uw privacy en verzamelen geen persoonlijke informatie over u of uw systeem.

	U kunt uw deelname aan het programma op elk gewenst moment stoppen door de pagina met Instellingen te bekijken."

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 Afin d'améliorer votre expérience d'utilisateur en ce qui concerne nos produits, nous mettons en place une version actualisée de notre Programme de Personnalisation et d'Amélioration de l'Expérience Utilisateur. 

	En participant à ce programme, vous vous verrez proposer une expérience utilisateur très personnalisée en ce qui concerne les publicités, et plus encore. En accord avec la politique de ce programme, l'application collectera de façon anonyme des données au sujet de votre téléphone et de l'utilisation que vous faites de notre application pour améliorer votre expérience. Les données sont collectées via Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, et Alibaba Umeng.

	Cette application personnalise votre expérience publicitaire par l'intermédiaire de Google Admob et Facebook Audience Network. En acceptant cette expérience publicitaire améliorée, vous verrez des publicités que Google Admob et Facebook Audience Network jugent plus pertinentes pour vous. Selon vos paramètres de confidentialité, Google et Facebook peuvent collecter et traiter des informations personnelles, telles que les identifiants d'appareils, les données de localisation, ainsi que d'autres données démographiques et d'intérêt vous concernant de façon à vous fournir cette expérience publicitaire personnalisée.

	En acceptant, vous confirmez avoir plus de 16 ans et vous souhaitez participer à notre Programme de Personnalisation et d'Amélioration de l'Expérience Utilisateur.

	Nous respectons votre vie privée et nous ne collecterons pas vos données personnelles ou celles de votre appareil.

	Vous pouvez arrêter votre participation à ce programme à tout moment en vous rendant sur la page Paramètres."

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 Para mejorar su experiencia con nuestro producto, presentamos nuestro Programa de mejora y personalización de la experiencia del usuario. Al participar en el programa, se le ofrecerá un plan con experiencias muy personalizadas, incluyendo publicidad individualizada y mucho más. Según la política del programa, esta app recopilará información anónima sobre su teléfono y la utilización de nuestra app para mejorar su experiencia con el mismo. Esta información se recopila mediante Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, y Alibaba Umeng.

	Esta aplicación personaliza tu experiencia de anuncios mediante Google Admob y Facebook Audience Network. Si aceptas esta experiencia de anuncios mejorada, verás anuncios que Google Admob y Facebook Audience Network consideran más relevantes para ti. Según tus ajustes de privacidad, Google y Facebook podrán recopilar y procesar datos personales tales como identificadores de dispositivos, datos de ubicación y otros datos demográficos y de interés sobre ti para proporcionar esta experiencia de anuncios personaliza.

	Si estás de acuerdo, confirmas que eres mayor de 16 años y le gustaría unirse a nuestro Programa de mejora y personalización de la experiencia del usuario.

	Respetamos tremendamente su privacidad, y no recopilaremos ninguna información personal sobre usted o su sistema.

	Puede dejar de participar en el programa en cualquier momento indicándolo en la página de Ajustes."

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 Al fine di migliorare l'esperienza dei clienti con i nostri prodotti, stiamo presentando il nostro Programma aggiornato per il Miglioramento e la Personalizzazione dell'Esperienza degli Utenti. Partecipando al programma, ti sarà offerto un piano con soluzioni altamente personalizzate, che includono annunci pubblicitari individualizzati e tanto altro. In base alla politica del programma, quest'app raccoglierà dati anonimi sul telefono dell'utente e sul relativo utilizzo dell'app, al fine di migliorarne l'esperienza complessiva. I dati vengono raccolti tramite Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, e Alibaba Umeng.

	Quest'app personalizza la tua esperienza pubblicitaria grazie a Google Admob e i Facebook Audience Network. Accettando questa esperienza pubblicitaria avanzata, visualizzerai gli annunci che Google Admob e i Facebook Audience Network ritengono più importanti per te. A seconda delle tue impostazioni sulla privacy, Google e i Facebook potranno raccogliere ed elaborare dati personali, quali gli ID del dispositivo, i dati sulla posizione ed altri dati demografici e informazioni di tuo interesse, per offrirti un'esperienza pubblicitaria personalizzata.

	Accettando confermi di avere più di 16 anni e ti piacerà iscriverti al nostro Programma per il Miglioramento e la Personalizzazione dell'Esperienza degli Utenti.

	Rispettiamo la privacy degli utenti nella maniera più assoluta e non raccoglieremo dati personali o relativi al sistema da questi utilizzato.

	Potrai interrompere la partecipazione al programma in qualsiasi momento, visitando la pagina Impostazioni."

"gdpr_dialog_desc" : "	 Para melhorarmos a sua experiência com o nosso produto, apresentamos o nosso Programa de Personalização e Melhoria da Experiência do Utilizador atualizado. Ao participar no programa, irá receber um plano de solução de experiência altamente personalizado, incluindo anúncios individualizados e muito mais. De acordo com a política do programa, esta app irá recolher informações anónimas sobre o seu telefone e a utilização da nossa app para melhorar a sua experiência com ela. A informação é recolhida através do Facebook Analytics, Google Firebase, e Alibaba Umeng.

	Este aplicativo personaliza a sua experiência por meio da Google Admob e Facebook Audience Netowork. Se você consentir com essa experiência de anúncios aprimorada, verá anúncios que a Google Admob e Facebook Audience Netowork acreditam ser os mais relevantes para você. Dependendo de suas configurações de privacidade, a Google e Facebook poderão coletar e processar dados pessoais, como identificadores de dispositivo, dados de localização e outros dados demográficos e de interesse a seu respeito com a finalidade de fornecer essa experiência de anúncios personalizada.

	Ao concordar, você confirma que tem mais de 16 anos de idade e você gostaria de participar no nosso Programa de Personalização e Melhoria da Experiência do Utilizador.

	Respeitamos muito a sua privacidade e não iremos recolher quaisquer informações pessoais suas ou do seu sistema.

	Pode deixar de participar no programa em qualquer momento, consultando a página de Definições."

playstore_details.title: Call Recorder - Automatic Call Recorder (NO-ROOT)
playstore_details.description:
Call Recorder, a free high-quality call recording app which gives you the easiest way to record all your phone calls, call conversations and no root needed.

Never worry about losing important call recordings! Record phone calls and save call recording with ease with this auto phone call recorder.This smart auto call recorder app is globally available helping thousands of users to record important phone calls from both sides.

By using Automatic Call Recorder, You can automatic record important calls and save any phone call you want, simple and smart. This Call Recorder can be used to record phone call, or record important calls from KAKAO, WhatsApp, Facebook, Line, Skype and more! 

Call Recorder  - Automatic Call Recorder (NO-ROOT) lets you easily record your incoming and outgoing phone calls from both sides.

►Call Recorder is an awesome advanced free call recorder application with these features:

- Easy to use
- Automatically record all incoming & outgoing calls, whenever and wherever
- High quality of the audio effect
- No root needed
- The most compatible tool with nearly all devices
- Organize your call records through call recorder
- Better support Pixel \ Samsung Galaxy S7 (Edge) \ Galaxy S8 (S8+) \  Galaxy S9 (S9+)

NO-ROOT NEEDED for Call Recorder
1. Record your calls automatically while calling.
2. You can play back, or save your call to mp3 files on your SD card and share to WhatsApp and Messenger with one click.
3. It’s FREE!

Record any phone call you want and choose which calls you to want to save by using the call recorder. You can set which calls are recorded and which are ignored. Listen to the recording, take notes and share it through auto call recorder.

There are three default settings for automatic recording by auto call recorder app:
Record everything (default) – This setting records all calls automatically except for contacts pre-selected to be ignored.
Ignore calls – This setting records no calls except for contacts pre-selected to be recorded.
Ignore contacts – This setting records all calls with people who are not contacts, except for contacts pre-selected to be recorded.

Auto call recorder allows you to record phone calls while on phone.
This automatic Call Recorder is a great Telephone Recording app for android,
Record any phone call you want, Choose which users or incoming\outgoing phone calls to record and choose which calls you want to save or share.

Other Key Features of Auto Call Recorder:
* Call Recorder automatic - record all your calls on auto-pilot.
* Easily manage all your recordings.
* Playback, or Share your phone recordings
* Sort recordings by names or group by dates.
* Reveal ID's of unknown callers automatically
* Search, sort and favorite your recordings
* High quality or the efficient file format of recordings

Try this reliable call recorder Now!
